---

# 🎮 Controls

| Key | Action |
|-----|-------|
| A / D | Move Player 1 |
| W | Jump Player 1 |
| Arrow Keys | Move Player 2 |
| ↑ | Jump Player 2 |
| ESC | Pause Menu |

---

# ▶️ Running the Game

1. Open the project folder in **VS Code**
2. Install the **Live Server** extension
3. Right-click `index.html`
4. Select **Open with Live Server**

The game will launch in your browser.

